  <datafield tag="545" ind1="1" ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Unit within University of Michigan Hospital responsible for education, activities, and recreation programs for hospitalized children.</subfield>
    <subfield code="b">Successor to the Hospital School which was established in 1922. Unit has received support from organizations such as Galens Medical Society, Kiwanis, and King's Daughters of Michigan.</subfield>
