  <datafield tag="520" ind1="2" ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Photographs, negatives, slides, films, and videotapes depicting Hospital School programs, activities, facilities, visitors, and events, including the Polio Ward, Christmas parties, hospitalized children engaged in education, play, and crafts; Galens wood shop, "Old Main" hospital, and C. S. Mott Children's Hospital. Includes photos and videotape of 1996 visit by Hillary Rodham Clinton.</subfield>
